__ Cantrip: Leap ______________________________ Cost: 10 _____________________

Use:  cantrip leap                              Material Component: none
Use:  C leap

The cantrip leap is a minor magic of the sphere of alteration.  When traced,
the caster is able to leap great heights in any direction which they could
normally travel.  To leap, the caster must type < leap [direction] >.  A fun
cantrip for the light of heart or exceedingly showy.
